history.text: Authorized changes to Chapter ENV.01 adding a new deer sustenance tag, allowing mentor hunting by 10- and 11-year olds, and clarifying required permits and fees for permittees who are minors. These changes are: amending subSection ENV.01.08(a)(2); amending subSection ENV.01.08(c)(1); amending subSection ENV.01.08(d); adding new subSection ENV.01.08(i); adding new subparts 21.8 (I)(1)-(4); adding new subsection 21.8 (J); adding new subparts 21.8 (J)(1)-(4) and amending subSection ENV.01.09(b)(2).
